im not a groomer

basically what happened was, despite me telling her to always be honest with me, she decided to lie about liking me s3xually, which led me to think she actually liked me like that. she then asked for nsfw pics of me to further make me believe this lie. wanting to make her happy, i obliged and sent some. she had never told me she was uncomfortable with this, despite me endlessly stressing to her that i always wanted her to be honest and to tell me when she was uncomfortable. also, she sent me some of her own nsfw back, which she all did voluntarily.

as for the whole ‚Äúlogan pressured her into it‚Äù thing, no i didnt. first off, i used to like to tease her with questionable things she said. she mistook this teasing as pressuring. and, i had always told her that i was only teasing her when i asked stuff like that, but she still decided to frame it as pressuring. not only that, but she would always contradict herself. before she ‚Äúadmitted‚Äù to liking me like that, she always vaguely implied she wanted to do (naughty activities) with me. so i had always asked for clarification and she would always say afterwards that she didnt actually like me like that, and then would go on to say something that contradicted that, which is why i always asked her if she liked me like that

delusions justifies her lying by saying she wanted to make me happy, but she knew that it would always make me more happy if she was honest with me rather than lying to me. that is one of the most important things i stressed in the relationship.

and also, just addressing some other somewhat unrelated accusations, i did not pressure her into becoming trans. i said that i would support her if she did and that i wouldnt break up with her if she did.

im not claiming she groomed me. i think we were both in the wrong and just hormonal at the time. i just wanted to show my side of the story.

to all meower users, im sorry i caused this stuff, i fucked up and this is the consequences, im so sorry for ruining it for all of you

delusions, if youre reading this, i still would like to discuss the situation with you. please, talk to me

anyways, here is her asking for nsfw. context: after she said she liked me s3xually i made a joke ab sending nsfw to her which lead to the following convo
